   <talk_paragraph index="n100_event_ilyn-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n100_event_ilyn-1-c" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I can use it as many times as I want?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Events Planner Irine$<BR>
There are two ways. You can either click <FONT color=#a94407>"Like!"</FONT> from the newly added menu that appears when you right-click on other players, or you can open Character window by pressing [<FONT color=#a94407>P</FONT>] and click Like History to return <FONT color=#a94407>"Like!"</FONT> to people who have given you <FONT color=#a94407>"Like!"</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
